        <p style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.25in;"><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Section 3Scope of Rights<span>………………………………………………………………………………………………………</span></span><span style="font-size: 11pt;">16</span></span></p>
